column5: Hi Everyone,  Just a quick note to wish you all every success in the coming Bass season.  Tight lines....  Colin.
Bass wishes to you as well catfish I can't wait to go
working saturday flipping river banks on sunday because boat still isn't running right, so I can put in, here in town and just use the electric all day
Me Neither, itching to get out there...
Hey Terry,  Work stops me getting out all this weekend as well I'm afraid but I'm going next weekend for sure, not sure where to go and with out a boat venues are limited.

I'm dying to get out but with a 12 ft tinny and a 9.9 I'm a little leary about going out on Cooch in this weather. Hope it clears up a bit later on. My 8 year old is driving me nuts because he can see othe rboats out on the water fishing!!!
I hope the weather improves and you can get out very soon.....
